Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.13,0:00:34.59,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Follow me Follow you　痛みでさえ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.84,0:00:36.39,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Follow me Follow you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.19,0:00:48.73,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}傷を負った　世界を知った
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.48,0:00:53.74,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}強く儚い果実
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.82,0:01:00.66,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}つきまとう　責任の重たさで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.99,0:01:05.16,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}熟れ落ちて　土へと還る
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:08.08,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Follow me Follow you　痛みでさえ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.13,0:01:10.84,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Follow me Follow you　通じ合えば
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.96,0:01:15.05,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}この血の滾りを解放してけ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:16.05,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}そこにいますか？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.18,0:01:20.97,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}衝突に戦々恐々　降り立つ堕天使
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.47,0:01:26.23,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}早々に早熟な実も　食らい尽くすの？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.81,0:01:31.94,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}もがく度に　蒼穹に聴いた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.11,0:01:35.15,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}君を確かめた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.15,0:01:35.98,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}あっけない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.98,0:01:39.78,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}無い無い　馴れ合い　有り余った慟哭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.33,0:01:45.12,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}葛藤に混乱していく　今を生きて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.41,0:01:52.00,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(960,3)}それでもまだ　僕らは目指した
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.92,0:01:53.55,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\fs45\pos(960,54)}Follow me Follow you　痛みでさえ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.55,0:01:56.17,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Follow me Follow you　通じ合えば
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.17,0:01:58.89,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Follow me Follow you　何処まででも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.89,0:02:00.35,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}Follow me Follow you
